snippet.textDisplay:
Hey there BA Test Kitchen Buds,

I so badly want to watch this series of videos, but I just cant get past the dinging, the tight shots of just Amiel's hands waving around the food, half effort attempts at cooking each method, and most horrifically the disturbing pretend chewing in the voiceover. I can just watch full episodes of Kitchen Nightmares for lessons on how to give 1/2 effort in Every Way. Please, I want to give you guys another chance. This is just so hard to watch. I'm at 11:48 and for the rest of the video I'm just going to turn the sound off, subtitles on, and see if that makes it better.



Please have Brad do these videos. I watch Bon Appetit videos only because of Brad's goofy antics. If he ever goes away I'm going away as well. I'd rather watch this series in parts than have every method sloppily crammed into one Scorsese length production.


With all that said, let me offer you BA TK Buds this, you guys to a great job and all of your quirkily endearing qualities are very redeeming.


- C
